{"tid":896774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"團體東涌圍堵旅行團　中國女領隊激動爆喊","createTime":"2018-11-10T10:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T15:01:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":363,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"7354ff5c421e5eefcba3a94e8c9ae4095832ca8b","tid":896774,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181110/photo/bkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181110173744\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181110%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181110173744&h=74c218b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181110/photo/bkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_02p.jpg?20181110173744\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181110%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20181110173744&h=2cdcb191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181110/photo/bkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_03p.jpg?20181110173744\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181110%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20181110173744&h=adf9d4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181110/photo/bkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_04p.jpg?20181110173744\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181110%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20181110173744&h=9ce1e3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東涌被內地旅行團攻陷，有本地團體今日(10日)下午在港鐵東涌站發起公民監察行動，圍堵內地旅行團，詢問其領隊是否有本地旅行社接待，及記錄所有大陸違規旅行社名稱，並點算數量。<br />\n<br />\n被圍堵女領隊聲稱有「地接」，但地接已離開，被團體質疑說謊，圍堵她不放行，要求她聯絡地接露面，女領隊激動爆喊，在警察查牌後護送上巴士離開。<br />\n<br />\n發起行動的荃灣區議員譚凱邦稱，觀察到東涌旅行團中，超過一半屬於黑工導遊帶領的內地旅行團，應予打擊。他反對有旅遊業界的建議，將大橋旅客分流到荃灣、葵青的建議，認為分流治標不治本，只將逼爆情況轉移，應限制這些違法內地團不能入境，或不能乘搭B6巴士。<br />\n<br />\n本地組織「東涌人Tung Chung Future 」主席王進洋表示，明天(11日)會將行動升級，預計有20至40人參與，主要打擊不明來歷旅行團，會準備橫額，包圍沒有地接的旅行團領隊等。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員兼東涌南區議員周浩鼎下午到東涌視察，他認為B6巴士站太近民居，人流聚集影響居民，要求緊急搬走。他又批評團體狙擊遊客行為具挑動及滋擾性，不能接受。但周的言論惹來站在附近的團體成員不滿，質問他「為何出賣東涌居民」，周需在警員護送下離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181110/bkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181110%2Fbkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001.html&d=MT3PDYCEpOChyhPV5aSm9AHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=2d3e1ab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181110/bkn-20181110163055850-1110_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"223f712c06ad3e7ff8472c05bc39d5aabf2997a5","tid":896774,"uid":38651,"like":177,"dislike":0,"score":177,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"啱呀 鬧下班大陸喱就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffeedefd7b8338e7e2616847eeed06f1c9d9497","tid":896774,"uid":117837,"like":261,"dislike":0,"score":261,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"T04\t東涌北\t傅曉琳\t\t新民黨\t<br />\nT05\t東涌南\t周浩鼎\t\t民建聯\t<br />\n共業嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84916a37c599ca3ab919be4d1acbf4c8956b42f2","tid":896774,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d528bf484617df86d4c2938405d02e051dbeb82c","tid":896774,"uid":133806,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"仲要做多少少嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04759b4f84e23a9ad472d2ab02d10880aba62034","tid":896774,"uid":133806,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><del>仲要</del>做多少少嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/